object.customQuery:
SELECT distinct application.SystemId, application.ParentId, application.CMMContainer, application.Id, application.UpdateCount, application.UpdateUser, application.UpdateTimestamp, application.ApplicationNumber, application.Version, application.CustomerRef, application.PolicyRef, application.Status, application.ChangeInfoRef, application.TypeCd, application.LockTaskId, application.Description, application.ExternalStateData, application.VIPLevel, application.AuditAccountRef, application.StatementAccountRef, application.PolicyScreenInd, application.UnderwritingScreenInd, application.LocationsScreenInd, application.RisksScreenInd, application.PropertyLineScreenInd, application.PropertyScreenInd, application.LiabilityScreenInd, application.LossHistoryScreenInd, application.AdditionalInterestsScreenInd, application.FormsScreenInd, application.ReviewScreenInd, application.ReinsuranceScreenInd, application.CommissionScreenInd, application.PremiumInfoScreenInd, application.WorksheetsScreenInd, application.SpecialOptionsScreenInd, application.CloseoutScreenInd, application.RowId 
FROM
 application  where application.CMMContainer='Application' and application.SystemId in (select SystemId from advrxxchangedbeans where CMMContainer='Application' AND 
concat(adddt,addtm)>='$$M_StartDt' and concat(adddt,addtm) <='$$M_EndDt' )
